column5: Looks like i can have the rest of the day off if i want it . "nice thing about being the boss" Any body want to jump in and go fishing for the rest of the day on Kempenfelt ? I can be at the Tiffin launch for 2:00 if i have to be . Sorry Brian but the devil made me do it .........lol .
no takers OK , i'll go roll asphalt for hour and check back then .
No time for fishing,you have gravel parking lots to mend.

Plus every thing else thats on my plate , got called back out with the excavator for an emeragency dig and now its go get the cat loader going that just died ... so much for going fishing  , see ya's........................
Damn! If I had have seen this yesterday, you would have had a taker! Haha!
if you find any time next week, ill be around after 4:30 most days.
keep your eyes on the board Miracon , it will probably come up again........
